quotes.quote: Big results require big ambitions.
What we call results are beginnings.
Forget about style; worry about results.
You cannot fail. You can only get results.
Excuses are useless. Results are priceless.
The only thing that follows work is results.
Infinite patience produces immediate results.
When you see the results, you forget the pain.
Great results, can be achieved with small forces.
Resolutions require only words. Results take action.
Good results when achieved make insults cease to exist.
Attention with intention gets results worthy of mention.
If you want different results, do not do the same things.
Fall in love with the process, and the results will come.
Remember, what you focus on expands; results follow focus.
The results of your life reflect the standards you've set.
We get real results only in proportion to the real values we give.
A successful person allows his results to speak for him, not his mouth.
If you want extraordinary results you must put in extraordinary effort.
Results are obtained by exploiting opportunities, not by solving problems.
Results take time to measure.
Positivity helps produce better results.
Positive thoughts lead to positive results.
Success results when preparation meets opportunity.
Your results are an expression of your level of awareness.
If we want better results, we have to make better choices.
The results of philanthropy are always beyond calculation.
Unexpected results are the rule rather than the exception.
Good order results spontaneously when things are let alone.
All your behavior results from the thoughts that precede it.
